<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَأَلَ سَائِلٌ}</span> ... دَعَا دَاعٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِعَذَابٍ وَاقِعٍ}</span> ... بِوُقُوعِ العَذَابِ عَلَيْهِمْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ذِي الْمَعَارِجِ}</span> ... صَاحِبِ العُلُوِّ وَالجَلَالِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَعْرُجُ}</span> ... تَصْعَدُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَالرُّوحُ}</span> ... جِبْرِيلُ - عليه السلام -.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{صَبْرًا جَمِيلًا}</span> ... لَا جَزَعَ فِيهِ، وَلَا شَكْوَى مِنْهُ لِغَيْرِ اللهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالْمُهْلِ}</span> ... مِثْلَ حُثَالَةِ الزَّيْتِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَالْعِهْنِ}</span> ... كَالصُّوفِ المَصْبُوغِ المَنْفُوشِ الَّذِي ذَرَتْهُ الرِّيحُ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{حَمِيمٌ}</span> ... قَرِيبٌ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُبَصَّرُونَهُمْ}</span> ... يُشَاهِدُ بَعْضُهُمْ بَعْضًا، وَيَعْرِفُهُ وَلَا يُكَلِّمُهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَفَصِيلَتِهِ}</span> ... عَشِيرَتِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تُؤْويهِ}</span> ... تَضُمُّهُ، وَيَنْتَمِي إِلَيْهَا.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَلَّا}</span> ... لَيْسَ الأَمْرُ كَمَا تَتَمَنَّاهُ أَيُّهَا الكَافِرُ مِنْ حُصُولِ الاِفْتِدَاءِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَظَى}</span> ... جَهَنَّمُ تَتَلَهَّبُ نَارُهَا، وَتَتَلَظَّى.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَزَّاعَةً لِّلشَّوَى}</span> ... تَنْزِعُ بِشِدَّةِ حَرِّهَا جِلْدَةَ الرَّاسِ، وَسَائِرَ أَطْرَافِ البَدَنِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَأَوْعَى}</span> ... أَمْسَكَ مَالَهُ فِي وِعَاءٍ، وَلَمْ يُؤَدِّ حَقَّ اللهِ فِيهِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>